{"title":"生气的陆家驹","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5071","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>Acheing:家驹~教我splay吧</p><p>陆家驹：no!</p><p>Acheing：家驹~</p><p>陆家驹：啦啦啦</p><p>Acheing：。。。恨！别逼我！</p><p>陆家驹：噢</p><p>——然后，我就利用黑科技关了他的电脑。。。</p><p>陆家驹很生气，一心想报复我（Acheing）</p><p>我自然很害怕，不得不去请他吃饭。</p><p>已知吃第i顿饭，陆家驹的饱涨度（暂且先这么说吧）为ai，生气值会减去bi。</p><p>当然，陆家驹也是人，也是有饭量的啦！</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\"></span>读入n,m,k。意为读入n个数，陆家驹的饭量为m，初始生气值为k。</p><p>第2至第n+1行，每行2个数，即ai，bi（见描述）。<br></p><p>接下来，帅气可爱的Acheing就要让你求出陆家驹的<span style=\"\">最小生气值</span>是多少。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出一个数，即陆家驹的最小生气值(可以有负数)。<br/></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2 3 5</p><p>1 2</p><p>2 3</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>0</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1&lt;=n&lt;=1000</p><p>1&lt;=m&lt;=1000</p><p>1&lt;=k&lt;=10000</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}